name: Taupō
description: Key lime, spanish cedar, and freshly zested orange. Medium straw hue, meringue-like foam. Hops: Riwaka, Wakatu and Citra.

name: Tides

name: Glyphs
description: Tangerine, orange zest, and aromatic pine.  Hops: BRU-1, Simcoe, Strata and Michigan Chinook.

name: Array

name: Elias
description: Smooth, subtle citrus notes and floral aroma.

name: Revada
type: Strawberry with Blueberry & Hibiscus Smoothie Sour
description: Thicc and tart, berry medley, bright. Vibrant pink and full bodied.
